<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<document xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="./Sample-file-4-xml.xsd">
	<title>Translating XML documents</title>
	<section>
		<heading>Simple sentences</heading>
		<p>This is a sentence.</p>
		<p>This is a new sentence.</p>
		<p>This is another new sentence.</p>
	</section>
	<section>
		<heading>Numbers</heading>
		<p>In this document there are 114 words. </p>
		<p>Sentence number 1 contains 4 words.</p>
		<p>This sentence contains a currency unit (1,500.00 USD).</p>
		<p>This sentence contains a date: December 12, 2011</p>
	</section>
	<section>
		<heading>Formatting</heading>
		<list>
			<li>This sentence contains an <u>underlined</u> word.</li>
			<li>This sentence contains a word in <b>bold</b> and one in <i>italics</i>.</li>
			<li>This sentence contains a <span class="important">word</span> in a character style.</li>
			<li>This sentence contains a manual<br/>line break.</li>
		</list>
	</section>
	<section>
		<heading>Repetitions</heading>
		<p>This is a new sentence.</p>
		<p>This is a <b>new</b> sentence.</p>
		<p>Sentence number 2 contains 5 words.</p>
	</section>
	<section>
		<heading>References</heading>
		<p>This sentence contains a footnote<xref id="1">(1)</xref>
		</p>
		<p>This sentence contains a <a href="http://www.wikipedia.org" title="Link to Wikipedia">hyperlink</a>.</p>
	</section>
	<references>
		<ref id="1">This is the text in the footnote.</ref>
	</references>
</document>
